419, \"to\": 2433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I feel like I knew straight away it wasn't enough, in diving you can kind of tell where or whereabouts the score is going to be at.\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"the score\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So for us, I think we knew, but at the same time you are still waiting for that scoreboard to pop up and show whether we have done it or not.\\\"\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2721, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2588}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2627}, {\"ngram\": \"that scoreboard\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2669}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Birthday tomorrow, I do not know what I am going to do,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 2723, \"to\": 2791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"See what's going on, maybe go and see Paris and have a bit of a celebration.\\\"\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2832, \"end\": 2837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999947453944, \"rank\": 5.25466030192473e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2852}, {\"ngram\": \"a celebration\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Harper said his daughter was \\\"very determined\\\" and would not be able to \\\"properly\\\" celebrate her 24th birthday until her Games is over, as she gears up for the individual 3m springboard event, which begins with the preliminaries on August 7.\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 3117, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mr Harper\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2882}, {\"ngram\": \"his daughter\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 2900}, {\"